{"url":"https://www.u-mart.co.jp/company_recruit_frute_.html","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n\t<head>\n\n<!-- WIKIPLUS auto-header start -->\n<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"application/xhtml+xml; charset=UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"INDEX,FOLLOW\" />\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"ユーマート,ニュース,お知らせ,東海道写楽,お知らせ,ニュース,おいしさが自慢,静岡包材,酒のuマート,uマート,静岡市,清水区,駿河区,葵区,スーパー,お持ち帰り,寿司\" />\n<meta name=\"Description\" content=\"只今、ユーマートの店舗正社員を募集中！活気のある職場で、あなたの元気を活かしませんか？\" />\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"ファミリーショップuマート\" />\n<meta name=\"Copyright\" content=\"株式会社ユーマート\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"wikiplus/wikiplus_system_preset.css?cf=495041\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/lib/fancybox/jquery.fancybox-1.3.4.css?cf=495041\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"modules/image/image.css\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"modules/mailform/mailform.css\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"modules/sitemap/sitemap.css\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"modules/timeline/timeline.css\" />\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n.input-item {\n    display: flex;\n    margin-left : 20px;\n    margin-right: 20px;\n    justify-content: space-around;\n}\n</style>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/jquery-1.7.1.min.js?cf=495041\"></script>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/jquery.json-2.2.min.js?cf=495041\"></script>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/jquery.csv-0.71.min.js?cf=495041\"></script>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/jquery.cookie.js?cf=495041\"></script>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"wikiplus/script/jquery/jquery.highlight-4.closure.js?cf=495041\"></script>\n<script charset=\"utf-8\" type=\"te